channel.title: Owner cape symbol
channel.description:
yea this is my second/third model (second model completed)
here is what it look like
[IMG]http://i280.photobucket.com/albums/kk170/xcvxcv2/crownfinished-1.jpg[/img]
here is what it looks like on a cape
[IMG]http://i280.photobucket.com/albums/kk170/xcvxcv2/crownwithcape-1.jpg[/img]
all credit goes to Da 0wnz for the cape
the symbol took me 3 hours to make
yes i know im really slow but slow is good
i also had a break for breakfast so that was maybe 30 mins
total the symbol took me 2 hours and 30 minutes
it took a while because i tried to make every line a right angle except for a few that needed to be 45 degree angles
it was hard but i will try to change the colors a bit more and make the lines a little more straight
heres what it looks like without the colors
[IMG]http://i280.photobucket.com/albums/kk170/xcvxcv2/crownblueprintlol-1.jpg[/img]
kk if a lot of people want me to release i will
i just dont know how to animate a cape yet so i cant release it with the cape (the cape isnt mine)
please post comments about it
